Package rajawali.materials.methods

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDiffuseMethod  
    ISpecularMethod  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiffuseMethod
    Contains a collection of diffuse shading methods.
    DiffuseMethod.Lambert
    Defines Lambertian reflectance.
    DiffuseMethod.Toon
    Toon shading or cel shading is a type of non-photorealistic rendering designed to make a model appear to be hand-drawn.
    SpecularMethod
    Contains a collection of diffuse shading methods.
    SpecularMethod.Phong
    Phong shading interpolates surface normals across rasterized polygons and computes pixel colors based on the interpolated normals and a reflection model.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DiffuseMethod.DiffuseShaderVar
    Defines shader variables that are specific to diffuse shading.
    SpecularMethod.SpecularShaderVar
    Defines shader variables that are specific to specular shading.
